Package: bright-findutils
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: GNU findutils with BrightDate time system
 GNU findutils patched to support BrightDate timestamps. Provides bfind,
 blocate, bupdatedb, and bxargs — BrightDate-aware counterparts to the
 standard GNU find utilities.
 .
 BrightDate is a decimal SI day count since J2000.0 (2000-01-01T12:00:00 TT)
 measured on the TAI timescale, with no leap-second discontinuities.
 .
 This package installs the bright variants only (bfind, blocate, bupdatedb,
 bxargs) and does not conflict with or replace the standard findutils package.
